The paper discusses the development of a system and software library for worst-case complexity analysis, which involves formal derivation of constraints and solving recurrence relations. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of Symbolic Computation (cs.SC), Programming Languages (cs.PL), Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS), Software Engineering (cs.SE), and Logic in Computer Science (cs.LO).
